00:17:14.140 --> 00:17:15.740
Saya rasa sepinggan udang kara sudah memadai.

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:16.599
Hei, kenapa kau memperlekehkan aku?

00:17:16.599 --> 00:17:17.560
